node.name: fantasy-la-liga-predictor
node.description: Fantasy La Liga Predictor is a machine learning model that provides users with player recommendations for the Spanish football league, La Liga, and a website for easy interaction with the model.

node.name: 2040-ape
node.description: A unique take on Gabriele Cirulli's popular 2048 game, offering a brain-computer interface experience that allows players to control the game using signals from the NeuroSky headset.

node.name: reciprep
node.description: Discovering new recipes and planning your meals has never been easier!

node.name: sudoku-solvers
node.description: A comprehensive collection of algorithms to solve the popular puzzle game, Sudoku.

node.name: go-fake-news
node.description: A website built at an AI Hackathon for detecting fake news using machine learning algorithms and user-inputted news articles.

node.name: MIBA-2023-CAPSTONE-RB-NLP
node.description: This project from ESADE MIBA students of team G03 in collaboration with Roland Berger Paris aims to develop a data ingestion pipeline for news article data and test different NLP approaches on the extracted data to analyze topics and trends linked to a particular brand or company name.
